schedulebot is a discord application written for the Goldwatch community.

currently supported commands:

help
schedule
cancel
list
show
signup
dropout

make go:

clone repo
install
  nodejs (developed against 6.9.5)
  npm
  mongodb
in repo dir do `npm update`
copy config.json.example to config.json and edit
create an unprivileged service user if you care about not getting hacked
  or don't
wrap the node process in a service if you care about reliability
  or don't

$ nodejs schedulebot.js
